sent: studentsfrom: vincent j. del casino, jr., provost and senior vp for academic affairsdear spartan students,i hope that you are well and safe! as you know, the semester at sjsu begins next week. the faculty have been preparing through anonline summer instituteto deliver some amazing courses this fall, and the staff on campus are very excited to support all the activities and clubs that are such important parts of the sjsu experience.i want to let you know that we have also created a resource center calledlearn anywherefor you to utilize throughout this academic year. this website provides a rich amount of information on preparing for your online courses this fall.highlights of information you can tap into from this resource center include:we hope that you will take advantage of this website resource to prepare yourself for classes next week. dont hesitate to reach out to our community should you need any further assistance. we are all here to help make the transition to the fall semester as smooth as possible!sincerely,dr. vincent j del casino jr.phone:408-924-2400email:provost@sjsu.educlark hall 552one washington squaresan jos, ca 95192-0020